---
title: Sweet & Spicy Mandarin Chicken with Crunchy Sesame Salad
description: Four ingredients, and ten minutes: That’s all you need to make this delicious dinner. (Seriously!) Chicken breast strips are browned, then simmered with spicy-sweet Thai chili sauce and mandarin orange juice until sticky. It’s all served over a salad that’s tossed with crunchy toppings and a nutty sesame dressing. Now that’s a dinner dream come true!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-spicy-mandarin-chicken-da58ea64.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-spicy-mandarin-chicken-5f8df9f6cd1cbf666463b5e4-ec6c35a5.pdf
